|-------|---------------|
| `gmail` | emails, inbox, reply, send |
| `google-calendar` | schedule, meeting, calendar, availability |
| `todo` | tasks, what's on my plate |
| `agent-browser` | browse, scrape, click, fill form |
| `maestro` | parallel tasks, scale output |

